As a Hongkonger now living in Taiwan. Traditional Chinese characters are my pride and also my daily interface with the surrounding.

The piece uses the locus along with the shape of Chinese characters [川], with a different perceive angle from 0-359 deg to view and calculate 6 different lengths in each locus, resulting in a real-time translation from character back to 360 unique generative creek compositions.

Chinese Calligraphy by ARNO LIN.

Bring some oriental essence to your collection now.

